Class ZipNode<OUT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robopupu.api.graph.Node<java.lang.Void,OUT>
      • com.robopupu.api.graph.nodes.ZipNode<OUT>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InputNode<java.lang.Void>, OutputNode<OUT>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Zip2Node, Zip3Node, Zip4Node, Zip5Node, Zip6Node, Zip7Node, Zip8Node, Zip9Node

    public abstract class ZipNode<OUT>
extends Node<java.lang.Void,OUT>
    AZipNode has 2 to 9 ZipInputNodes from which it receives input values and combines them to produce an output value using a provided Function. ZipNode is an abstract base class for concrete classes: Zip2Node, Zip3Node, Zip4Node, Zip5Node, Zip6Node, Zip7Node, Zip8Node, and Zip9Node.
